WEBVTT

00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:05.305
(Muzika)

00:00:05.855 --> 00:00:10.389
Danijel Hedli: Doživotna u Pensilvaniji
upravo to i znači,

00:00:10.610 --> 00:00:14.302
doživotna bez mogućnosti na pomilovanje.

00:00:14.302 --> 00:00:16.182
Za nas doživotne,

00:00:16.182 --> 00:00:18.411
kako same sebe nazivamo,

00:00:18.411 --> 00:00:20.455
jedina šansa za otpuštanje

00:00:20.455 --> 00:00:22.684
jeste kroz zamenu sudske kazne,

00:00:22.684 --> 00:00:27.304
koja je bila odobrena
samo dvema ženama od 1989,

00:00:27.304 --> 00:00:30.105
pre, skoro, 30 godina.